# UI Handoff Contract — VibeStack UI → Backend

## UI Stack (already in /ui)
- React 19, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind v4, React Router
- UI fetch hook: /api/updates, with a mock fallback if API unavailable

## API Contract (must implement)
GET /api/updates

Query params:
- query (string, optional)
- source_type (string, optional; UI may pass "All" — treat as unset)
- source_name (string, optional; UI may pass "All" — treat as unset)
- tag (string, optional; UI may pass "All" — treat as unset)
- sort ("newest" | "top_score", optional; default newest)
- page (int, optional; default 1)
- pageSize (int, optional; default 10)

Response:
{
  "items": [{
    "id": number,
    "source_name": string,
    "source_type": string,
    "title": string,
    "url": string,
    "published_at": string (ISO),
    "short_description": string,
    "tags": string[],
    "internal_score": number
  }],
  "page": number,
  "pageSize": number,
  "total": number
}

## Non-negotiables (V1)
- Locked schema (updates, newsletter_sends)
- Deterministic ingestion (no LLM)
- No user accounts / personalization
- Cron ingestion every 8 hours; newsletter weekly Top 5
